			<h2>About My Work</h2>
			<p>My process begins with understanding: the audience, the goals, and the mood a project needs to evoke. From there, I move through research, testing, and refinement, allowing the work to evolve naturally. Each project becomes a lesson in creativity and craft, helping me grow sharper, more thoughtful, and more intentional.</p>
