				<h3>Collected - Music Blog</h3>
				<a href="projects2/music_blog/index.html" target="_blank">Go to Website</a>
				<p>For Collected, I explored a more refined expression of my personal design style through layout, imagery, typography, and color. The result is a clean, intentional composition that supports the overall mood while maintaining clarity and usability. Working with a music-focused theme allowed me to integrate both thoughtful visual decisions and expressive written content. This project strengthened my ability to balance creative freedom with a cohesive, audience-focused design approach.</p>
