				<h3>Yum Yum Kitchen</h3>
				<a href="projects2/yumyum/index.html" target="_blank">Go to Website</a>
				<p>In developing Yum Yum Kitchen, I focused on creating flexible layout structures that accommodate a variety of content types, from recipes to feature posts. The design emphasizes clarity, easy navigation, and a framework that supports frequent updates—mirroring the needs of an active food blog. This project strengthened my understanding of information architecture and building user-friendly, scalable web </p>
