			<div class="slide-text">
				<h3>Based Magazine</h3>
				<a href="projects2/BasedMagazine.pdf" target="_blank">View Full Magazine</a>
				<p>Based Magazine allowed me to explore a wide range of editorial techniques, from dynamic layouts to experimental typography, color, and imagery. Throughout the project, I developed a cohesive visual identity inspired by vintage skate magazines, grunge culture, and bold, expressive storytelling. This piece reflects significant growth in my editorial design skills, particularly in branding, advertising layouts, and long-form content structure. The final result embodies my personal style—raw yet refined, energetic yet intentional—capturing the garage-inspired aesthetic I set out to create. </p>
			</div>	
