			<div class="slide-text">
				<h3>Birthday Card Design</h3>
				<a href="projects2/card.pdf" target="_blank">View PDF</a>
				<p>For this project, I aimed to create a birthday card that felt distinctive while retaining the celebratory essence of traditional cards. Noticing that many cards follow predictable themes, I explored a moodier and slightly darker aesthetic to appeal to friends and family who resonate with alternative or unconventional styles. This approach allowed me to showcase my illustrative and storytelling skills while considering audience connection and emotional resonance. The design balances playfulness with depth, reflecting my ability to craft work that is both visually engaging and thoughtfully targeted.</p>
